{"tid":1535364,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[中立]我係一個中立L","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:37:08.000Z","uid":53352,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f1095a410ba96c85298f40bcdbc376a80a3a41e2","tid":1535364,"uid":53352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"大家聽我講句<br />\n我就無咩政治立場<br />\n見到d示威者咁樣又真係唔係好啱既<br />\n不過我見到d警察咁暴力真係覺得過左火囉<br />\n我就兩邊都唔幫既<br />\n但係你拉班示威者還拉幫示威者<br />\n又整斷人隻手又係咁扑人地個頭<br />\n見到d示威者流哂血人地呀爸呀媽都心痛架嘛<br />\n你都唔想你地既小朋友俾學校俾d老師指派既風紀打到爆哂缸架嘛<br />\n點都要賠下錢俾人<br />\n警察既然好似我咁政治中立就唔好去理d政治事件<br />\n有咩遊行集會都唔好出現啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"344154c9a878ba350664ffd94766481af09dff52","tid":1535364,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36c310092bee0c366f624db0ec623bf3a84cd8ef","tid":1535364,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:37:08.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a h